<h1>Edgemont Calgary Real Estate and Homes for Sale</h1>
<p>Edgemont offers a tranquil lifestyle with easy access to natural green spaces and parks. The noise levels in this area of the city are very low, making it the ideal place for relaxed, slow-paced living.</p>
<p>Edgemont has a large amount of woodland and outdoor areas. Many residences overlook Nose Hill Park and there are extensive biking trails. Many of the estate homes are situated on the brink of a vertical cliff with spectacular views of Calgary's cityscape and the mountains to the west.</p>

